        <para id="id19856462">_____________________________________ </para>
        <para id="id17947172">Professor Prove-It has confused the process of germination. Please help him rearrange the sentences in the correct order:</para>
        <list id="id17697538" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>The radicle appears first and grows downwards.</item>
          <item>The cotyledons absorb water and swell.</item>
          <item>The stem grows upwards and the leaves turn green.</item>
          <item>The seed-coat bursts open.</item>
          <item>Lateral roots develop on the radicle.</item>
          <item>Two small leaves appear when the cotyledons burst open.</item>
        </list>
